OOC: crap sent a blank one.

::Aerotaur::
       He answers his comlink halfheartedly.  "Sir, I mean no disrespect but 
I'm a bit out of range to make it to your briefing.  And... I have some 
matters to attend to.  If there is an emergency Windlord will know where to 
find me."  With that he turns off his comlink and trudges into the depths of 
his cave home.  At the very back he notices a small opening that he had not 
noticed during his previous tours.  Curious he makes his way inside.

--part1_19b.10f45be5.2b805d51_boundary
